OL,3,COlder private renter was 'three days
OL,4,Cfrom becoming homeless'
OL,6,FOlder people renting in the private
OL,7,Fsector in Northern Ireland are facing
OL,8,Fa "hidden housing crisis" in later
OL,9,Flife.
OL,11,FThat's according to a new report by
OL,12,Fthe Commissioner for Older People for
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,15,FThe report said many older people are
OL,16,Ffacing a combination of insecurity,
OL,17,Frising costs and unsuitable housing
OL,18,Fwhich risks becoming a major social
OL,19,Fissue in the years ahead.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
