PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1779372669
OL,3,COlder private renter was 'three days
OL,4,Cfrom becoming homeless'
OL,6,FThere are currently around 17,600
OL,7,Fpeople aged 65 and over who are
OL,8,Fprivate renters.
OL,10,FCommissioner Siobhan Casey warned the
OL,11,Fnumber is growing and could increase
OL,12,Fsignificantly by 2040.
OL,14,FThe research highlights how older
OL,15,Fprivate renters experience age-
OL,16,Fspecific challenges in the private
OL,17,Frented sector, leaving them exposed to
OL,18,Ffinancial strain, poor living
OL,19,Fconditions and the threat of losing
OL,20,Ftheir home.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
