OL,3,COlder private renter was 'three days
OL,4,Cfrom becoming homeless'
OL,6,FJan Branch has been a private renter
OL,7,Ffor over three decades and has been
OL,8,Fevicted three times.
OL,10,FThe 81-year-old told UTV "I was given
OL,11,Fnotice just before Christmas on- on
OL,12,Fthe first two occasions, and I had
OL,13,Ffour weeks over Christmas and New Year
OL,14,Fto find somewhere.
OL,16,F"Last time I was evicted was more
OL,17,Fdifficult because three days before I
OL,18,Fbecame homeless, I actually then found
OL,19,Fsomewhere."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
