OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1779372669
OL,3,COlder private renter was 'three days
OL,4,Cfrom becoming homeless'
OL,6,FMs Casey, said: "This report shines a
OL,7,Flight on a group that up until now,
OL,8,Fhave been overlooked.
OL,10,F"Older private renters face a unique
OL,11,Fand deeply concerning set of
OL,12,Fchallenges. They are navigating an
OL,13,Finsecure and increasingly expensive
OL,14,Fhousing market at a stage of life when
OL,15,Fstability is most important," she
OL,16,Fadded.
OL,18,F"At the same time, many are living on
OL,19,Ffixed incomes, managing health
OL,20,Fconditions, and in homes that do not
OL,21,Fmeet their needs."
