OL,3,COlder private renter was 'three days
OL,4,Cfrom becoming homeless'
OL,6,FThe report calls for action to
OL,7,Fstrengthen protections for private
OL,8,Frenters and ensure housing is safe,
OL,9,Fsecure and suitable for an ageing
OL,10,Fpopulation.
